    "updated_at": "2015-03-04T10:42:26Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Even with #7547 closed, I'm still keeping the `Easy` label, because I gave a solution in my last comment.\nI also want to add (regarding the target losing): Once you discover that the target is not visible (if it is an actor - `TargetType.Actor`) create a new target with `TargetType.Terrain` at the actual target's last known coordinates.\nNote: `TargetType.FrozenActor` might need some considering.\nAlso this won't fix the turret issue, so it's worth to do that ^ only if the actor `HasTrait<IMove>`. Otherwise just do `Target = null` or something, so the turret actually loses the target.\n\nI'd really like to see #7547 back with this addition so we can properly fix both issues.\n"
  },
